{"tid":885391,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"睇呢個中國youtuber 睇到哭jor  希望佢唔好被中共迫害","createTime":"2018-11-01T09:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T11:47:31.000Z","uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"235cd222bdb94ba1b9f6925dc19324b8b7b8d147","tid":885391,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:39:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=caEcUq1MGxI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcaEcUq1MGxI&d=p2QXTXhCRXikvMPatE8OWozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=19cbe315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=caEcUq1MGxI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p0OarnK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp0OarnK.png&h=047252fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f3f03b4983035e42232fddf8e2d5dae5aa65661","tid":885391,"uid":150609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:41:33.000Z","msg":"家人朋友都被公安拜訪關切了，<br />\n<br />\n這幾天經歷太多了，父母親人，同事，領導，老師，同學，幾乎我生活中的所有人都聯繫<br />\n我了。 <br />\n1.勸我認錯，停止言論。這才讓我明白事情的嚴重性。<br />\n2.覆水難收。我已經無能為力，我管不了臺灣媒體怎麼說。因為這是他們有言論自由。<br />\n3.沒想到這視頻傳播這麼快。我在國內也發過類似觀點的視頻，也講過:獨裁，民主，言<br />\n論自由等話題。 <br />\n4.感謝關心支持我的人。<br />\n5.對於國內許多謾駡甚至恐嚇，反正我管不了你們的嘴，你們愛怎麼說怎麼說。<br />\n6.海峽兩岸事實上分治，兩邊的政府誰都管不了誰了。我說的是事實。<br />\n7.高曉松在一期《奇葩說》中說:臺灣比我們有更多的自由。現在我深刻體會了他的話，<br />\n那就是言論自由。"},{"pid":"2e75cb0f0e9dac2616715df69fb1c57eb9723c42","tid":885391,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:44:31.000Z","msg":"開錯動物台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281ccc2090d2066aa3cc375bf0d21d2a090dc004","tid":885391,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:23:46.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"8a5c0e9f0dfca70c13421cfe7c3d8e5f7c153c9f","tid":885391,"uid":197162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T11:47:31.000Z","msg":"め